e Airport|Milan\u2013Linate]], [[Milan Malpensa Airport|Milan\u2013Malpensa]], [[Montr\u00e9al\u2013Pierre Elliott Trudeau International Airport|Montr\u00e9al\u2013Trudeau]], [[Moscow Domodedovo Airport|Moscow\u2013Domodedovo]], [[Sheremetyevo International Airport|Moscow\u2013Sheremetyevo]], [[Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj International Airport|Mumbai]], [[Munich Airport|Munich]], [[Jomo Kenyatta International Airport|Nairobi\u2013Jomo Kenyatta]], [[Nashville International Airport|Nashville]], [[Lynden Pindling International Airport|Nassau]], [[Newark Liberty International Airport|Newark]], [[Newcastle International Airport|Newcastle upon Tyne]], [[Louis Armstrong New Orleans International Airport|New Orleans]], [[John F. Kennedy International Airport|New York\u2013JFK]], [[Nice C\u00f4te d'Azur Airport|Nice]], [[Kansai International Airport|Osaka\u2013Kansai]], [[Oslo Airport, Gardermoen|Oslo\u2013Gardermoen]], [[Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris\u2013Charles de Gaulle]], [[Philadelphia International Airport|Philadelphia]], [[Phoenix Sky Harbor International Airport|Phoenix\u2013Sky Harbor]], [[Pisa International Airport|Pisa]], [[Pittsburgh International Airport|Pittsburgh]], [[Portland International Airport|Portland (OR)]] (begins 1 June 2020),<ref>{{cite web |title=BRITISH AIRWAYS PUTS PORTLAND, OREGON, ON ITS ROUTE MAP |url=https://mediacentre.britishairways.com/pressrelease/details/86/2019-319/11920 |accessdate=18 December 2019}}</ref> [[Prague V\u00e1clav Havel Airport|Prague]], [[Keflav\u00edk International Airport|Reykjav\u00edk\u2013Keflav\u00edk]], [[Rio de Janeiro\u2013Gale\u00e3o International Airport|Rio de Janeiro\u2013Gale\u00e3o]], [[King Khalid International Airport|Riyadh]], [[Leonardo da Vinci\u2013Fiumicino Airport|Rome\u2013Fiumicino]], [[San Diego International Airport|San Diego]], [[San Francisco International Airport|San Francisco]], [[San Jose International Airport|San Jose (CA)]], [[Arturo Merino Ben\u00edtez International Airport|Santiago de