axing International Airport|Beijing\u2013Daxing]] (begins 13 July 2020),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/288850/china-southern-schedules-a380-beijing-daxing-london-heathrow-service-from-june-2020/ |title=China Southern schedules A380 Beijing Daxing \u2013 London Heathrow service from June 2020 |publisher=Routesonline |date= |accessdate=2020-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=China Southern delays Beijing Daxing \u2013 London Heathrow launch to mid-July 2020 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/290404/china-southern-delays-beijing-daxing-london-heathrow-launch-to-mid-july-2020/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=20 March 2020}}</ref> [[Guangzhou Baiyun International Airport|Guangzhou]], [[Sanya Phoenix International Airport|Sanya]] (ends 18 June 2020),<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=China Southern revises London service from June 2020 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/288876/china-southern-revises-london-service-from-june-2020/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=20 January 2020}}</ref> [[Wuhan Tianhe International Airport|Wuhan]] (suspended; ends 10 July 2020),<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=China Southern Wuhan \u2013 London S20 service changes as of 07APR20 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/290673/china-southern-wuhan-london-s20-service-changes-as-of-07apr20/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=7 April 2020}}</ref> [[Zhengzhou Xinzheng International Airport|Zhengzhou]] \n<!-- -->\n| [[Croatia Airlines]] | [[Zagreb Airport|Zagreb]]<br>'''Seasonal:''' [[Split Airport|Split]] \n<!-- -->\n| [[Delta Air Lines]] | [[Hartsfield\u2013Jackson Atlanta International Airport|Atlanta]], [[Logan International Airport|Boston]], [[Detroit Metropolitan Airport|Detroit]], [[Minneapolis\u2013Saint Paul International Airport|Minneapolis/St. Paul]], [[John F. Kennedy International Airport|New York\u2013JFK]], [[Salt Lake City International Air