in Airport|Dublin]]||align='right'|1,855,333||{{increase}} 2.5%\n|-\n|4||{{flagdeco|Netherlands}} [[Amsterdam Airport Schiphol|Amsterdam]]||align='right'|1,748,216||{{increase}} 0.1%\n|-\n|5||{{flagdeco|Hong Kong}} [[Hong Kong International Airport|Hong Kong]]||align='right'|1,612,530||{{increase}} 2.6%\n|-\n|6||{{flagdeco|US}} [[Los Angeles International Airport|Los Angeles]]||align='right'|1,602,892||{{decrease}} 3.3%\n|-\n|7||{{flagdeco|Germany}} [[Frankfurt Airport|Frankfurt]]||align='right'|1,548,995||{{decrease}} 0.7%\n|-\n|8||{{flagdeco|Singapore}} [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]]||align='right'|1,526,634||{{increase}} 7.4%\n|-\n|9||{{flagdeco|Spain}} [[Adolfo Su\u00e1rez Madrid\u2013Barajas Airport|Madrid]]||align='right'|1,476,551||{{increase}} 4.2%\n|-\n|10||{{flagdeco|Germany}} [[Munich Airport|Munich]]||align='right'|1,266,993||{{increase}} 2.0%\n|-\n|11||{{flagdeco|Qatar}} [[Hamad International Airport|Doha]]||align='right'|1,264,687||{{increase}} 7.0%\n|-\n|12||{{flagdeco|France}} [[Paris Charles de Gaulle Airport|Paris CDG]]||align='right'|1,260,985||{{increase}} 0.8%\n|-\n|13||{{flagdeco|US}} [[O'Hare International Airport|Chicago\u2013O'Hare]]||align='right'| 1,250,426||{{increase}} 7.9%\n|-\n|14||{{flagdeco|Switzerland}} [[Zurich Airport|Zurich]]||align='right'| 1,188,545||{{increase}} 1.8%\n|-\n|15||{{flagdeco|UAE}} [[Abu Dhabi International Airport|Abu Dhabi]]||align='right'|1,158,732||{{increase}} 10.8%\n|-\n|16||{{flagdeco|Canada}} [[Toronto Pearson International Airport|Toronto\u2013Pearson]]||align='right'|1,119,673||{{increase}} 5.5%\n|-\n|17||{{flagdeco|US}} [[San Francisco International Airport|San Francisco]]||align='right'|1,075,554||{{increase}} 1.9%\n|-\n|18||{{flagdeco|Switzerland}} [[Geneva Airport|Geneva]]||align='right'|1,070,524||{{increase}} 1.3%\n|-\n|19||{{flagdeco|US}} [[Miami International Airport|Miami]]||align='right'|1,069,986||{{increase}} 3.9%\n|-\n|20||{{flagdeco|Turkey}} [[Istanbul New Airport|Istanbul]]||align='