OG|1980}} || 101 || 6 || 4 || 2 || '''12''' || style=\"background:#ffdab9;\"|[[1980 Winter Olympics medal table|3]] || style=\"background:#ffdab9;\"|[[1980 Winter Olympics medal table|3]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|1984}} || 107 || 4 || 4 || 0 || '''8''' || style=\"background:#ffdab9;\"|[[1984 Winter Olympics medal table|3]] || [[1984 Winter Olympics medal table|4]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|1988}} || 118 || 2 || 1 || 3 || '''6''' || [[1988 Winter Olympics medal table|9]] || [[1988 Winter Olympics medal table|9]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|1992}} || 147 || 5 || 4 || 2 || '''11''' || [[1992 Winter Olympics medal table|5]] || [[1992 Winter Olympics medal table|6]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|1994}} || 147 || 6 || 5 || 2 || '''13''' || [[1994 Winter Olympics medal table|5]] || [[1994 Winter Olympics medal table|5]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|1998}} || 186 || 6 || 3 || 4 || '''13''' || [[1998 Winter Olympics medal table|5]] || [[1998 Winter Olympics medal table|6]]\n|- style=\"border: 3px solid red\"\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|2002}} || 202 || 10 || 13 || 11 || '''34''' || style=\"background:#ffdab9;\"|[[2002 Winter Olympics medal table|3]] || style=\"background:#dce5e5;\"|[[2002 Winter Olympics medal table|2]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|2006}} || 211 || 9 || 9 || 7 || '''25''' || style=\"background:#dce5e5;\"|[[2006 Winter Olympics medal table|2]] || style=\"background:#dce5e5;\"|[[2006 Winter Olympics medal table|2]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|2010}} || 216 || 9 || 15 || 13 || '''37''' || style=\"background:#ffdab9;\"|[[2010 Winter Olympics medal table|3]] || style=\"background:#f7f6a8;\"|[[2010 Winter Olympics medal table|1]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|2014}} || 230 || 9 || 9 || 10 || '''28''' || [[2014 Winter Olympics medal table|4]] || style=\"background:#dce5e5;\"|[[2014 Winter Olympics medal table|2]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|WOG|2018}} || 242 || 9 || 8 || 6 || '''23''' || |[[2018 Winter Olympics med